::Prowl::

From Iron Raptor thoughts, Prowl picked up the fact that his wing was 
broken. He moves it, seeing if it was, and is rewarded by a jolt of 
pain. He smiles slightly as she rubs his side.

-Of course I can stay awake,- he replies to her, excited at the idea 
of getting his and Epyon's plan underway. With the new spaceship 
behind him, that plan had just gotten better.
